1
00:00:00,960 --> 00:00:02,919
Song Youhua, I know you too well.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:04,440
You act stubborn,

3
00:00:04,519 --> 00:00:05,839
but deep down you're afraid I'll break up with you.

4
00:00:05,839 --> 00:00:07,000
You're terrified.

5
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,720
I won't hold it against you this time.

6
00:00:08,720 --> 00:00:10,160
But remember this lesson.

7
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:11,279
Don't do it again.

8
00:00:12,839 --> 00:00:14,240
Wash my clothes for me.

9
00:00:14,599 --> 00:00:15,919
Then go make a bowl of noodles.

10
00:00:15,919 --> 00:00:17,280
I want to eat when I get back from my shower.

11
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,280
Didn't I tell you to bring a family member?

12
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:23,879
If something goes wrong in surgery,

13
00:00:23,879 --> 00:00:25,000
there won't even be anyone to sign.

14
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,600
Your brother has an heir now.

15
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:28,199
Aren't you happy?

16
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,559
Your stomach pain is just a minor problem.

17
00:00:30,559 --> 00:00:32,240
Can it hurt more than Youping's legs?

18
00:00:34,439 --> 00:00:35,600
I'm an orphan.

19
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,000
I have no family.

20
00:00:59,439 --> 00:01:03,439
Happy birthday to you.

21
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,519
Make a wish.

22
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,920
Youhua, why isn't your brother here yet?

23
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:16,439
Youping, over here.

24
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:20,920
Youping.

25
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:21,920
This is your future sister-in-law,

26
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,840
Li Jiaojiao.

27
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:35,400
Fortunately, the tumor is benign.

28
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,879
You got your life back.

29
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:37,640
After you go home,

30
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,560
rest well.

31
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:39,840
Do not get upset.
